In this weeks episode of the Oregon Womens Basketball Podcast Sports Editor Shawn Medow brings sports reporters Sierra Webster Maggie Vanoni and Bryce Dole into the podcast studio PERIOD They discuss how the team has made it to the Pac12 Championship game for the second time Oregons loss and performance against Stanford and what they think would make for a successful season for the Ducks PERIOD
